Alex. A. AVILA v. UNITED STATES. No. 7920. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. June 8, 1936. James E. Fenton, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. Peirson M..Hall, U. S. Atty., of Los An-, geles, Cal.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, and of appellant, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
